snippet.title: Three Goblin Wobblin' - Announcement Trailer (Demo Available)
snippet.description:
WISHLIST AND PLAY THE DEMO NOW:
store.steampowered.com/app/2559860/Three_Goblin_Wobblin/

Goblins are prohibited from entering a local tavern, but luckily, they hatched a cunning plan. Move and balance the three goblins to help them quench their thirst and end goblin discrimination in this cute casual wobbling simulator.
